# Files that must NOT be uploaded as Cloudflare static assets.
# The build runs `wrangler deploy` with the repo root as the assets
# directory, so exclude VCS/tooling files (the .git pack exceeds the
# 25 MiB per-asset limit) and config that should not be served.
.git
.git/**
node_modules
node_modules/**
.gitignore
.assetsignore
wrangler.jsonc
wrangler.toml
*.map
README.md
